Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:35.45,Shadow house-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(363,519)\pos(1538,884)\c&H739FB8&}「露面」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:37.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,以上  也就是说亡灵骚乱的起因是设备故障
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,话虽如此  但要是你们疏忽了  同样的事还会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,给我继续打起精神来  解散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:49.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,看见芭比刚刚那副不甘心的样子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:53.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,处理黑灰的中间设施什么的  我和萝丝可都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那是归戴星人偶管的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,难道不是芭比自己疏忽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:59.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可  干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:04.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,和米娅交换的信帮了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:08.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没想到你会用自己做的人偶来回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:09.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我还不怎么会写字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,所以就用手工来回礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,大家  差不多到回房间的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:18.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是啊  要快点回去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:19.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:20.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真的好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,莎拉小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,明天就是「露面」？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.65,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因为埃米莉可很忙  所以没能告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也没能两个人一起学习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你打算用那副表情去「露面」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,今天的打扫就到这里  快点去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:03.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:06.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,现在埃米莉可的任务就是睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我知道了  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:14.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:24.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:31.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,悲伤点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,刚才那是干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:43.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,已经没事了  快点去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我只会给凯特小姐添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也理解不了凯特小姐的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:03.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,米娅对莎拉小姐的事情了如指掌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:15.48,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,莎拉小姐  请给予我成长的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,黏着物…凯特小姐说过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:39.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,黏着物是怀着恶意行动的黑灰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:42.97,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,积攒的黑灰经过一段时间就会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,小面包没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:50.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不过这么久了它也没有自己动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:55.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,里面有凯特小姐的意识所以没关系  就当作是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不能到公馆外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:04.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,外面有人吗  会遇到他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:10.37,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要是当了戴星人偶  说不定就能知道更多事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那目标就是当上戴星人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:19.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,莎拉我们必须戴上星星才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:24.17,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,会被伟大的祖父大人所认同的是莎拉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:29.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,还没「露面」呢  现在可不是与失败品一起玩的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,米娅只会为了莎拉而行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,米娅为了让莎拉变得闪耀而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因为米娅很优秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐想要成为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.65,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,果然还是想成为戴星人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在那之前  要先「露面」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:06:00.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在「露面」中落选的话  我一定会被处理掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也见不到凯特小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.97,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐有朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她喜欢做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:15.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我对凯特小姐一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:21.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我想通过「露面」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:24.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我说  尚恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  乔恩少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.32,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,明天就是「露面」了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,连续巡逻了几天  你也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不用打扫了  去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我还不能去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:37.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为了主人完成打扫是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:44.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你的主人乔恩在叫你去休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:48.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可是当乔恩少爷的房间脏兮兮时  我也不能休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你还是一如既往地顽固啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:53.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,而且你最近没戴眼镜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,明明在房间里会戴着的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为了习惯所以才不戴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:00.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,而且我的耳朵和鼻子都很灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,打扫狭窄的地方时我会戴上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,乔恩少爷为什么戴眼镜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,终于提到我的眼镜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:13.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我让无面人偶准备了和尚恩一样的眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这样子尚恩戴上眼镜也没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:20.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,乔恩少爷来配合我可就本末倒置了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:24.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,明明乔恩都让步了  你这说的什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:29.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是  我要是做了不符活人偶职责的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可能会在「露面」中获得不好的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:34.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,确实  正如尚恩所说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:38.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,戴眼镜就算了吧  不过你要去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:42.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,起码实现乔恩两个愿望中的一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:43.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,乔恩也差不多去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,晚安  乔恩少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:14.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,结果一次都没能给夏丽小姐送上晚安吻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:19.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,明天在「露面」中落选  这样的生活也就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,拉姆你觉得这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没关系的  拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因为谁都不会在意我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:36.41,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为什么现在才和感觉能成为朋友的孩子相遇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:41.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,丢脸玩意  没用鬼和…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:43.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,还有一个是什么来着  利奇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:46.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是花田  帕利克少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:54.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那样的对手  只会成为我们的陪衬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:58.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,还有一个是废物萝丝小组里的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但她也没什么了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:04.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也就是说  明天「露面」上值得期待的就只有帕利克了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:07.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,利奇  你是张好「脸」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克能戴上星星的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,然后被伟大的祖父大人疼爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:15.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你要把挡路的家伙都踢走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要尽快扔掉影宅的包袱才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:22.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克会在「露面」时挑选出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你会帮忙吗  利奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:27.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,当然  帕利克少爷挑出来的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我会干净利落地处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:32.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,利奇  就是这副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这才是帕利克的「脸」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:38.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,藐视匍匐在地上的家伙  这样的表情可不要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,早上的打扫结束了吧  露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快点让我给你打扮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好像「露面」后不仅会为我们画肖像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,还会拍照片装裱起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,稍微化下妆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,啊  真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:02.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露薏丝的「脸」变得这么漂亮  我好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露你也这么认为吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,当然  露薏丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:11.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,多细腻的皮肤啊  好想直接摸一摸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,重新化妆吧  得快点弄干净
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要盖上黑纱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.48,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是啊  还没「露面」所以要遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:39.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,初次见面  我是爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:43.24,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我住在祖父大人那一栋  是特别的活人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:47.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,和祖父大人住一栋…特别的活人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:51.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,来  让我带你们去露面厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我向活人偶提问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:06.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为什么连通祖父大人那一栋的这条走廊会这么长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为了警戒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:11.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,让高贵的大人们能安全生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:14.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这不是活人偶该考虑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也是有优秀的活人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好了  开始「露面」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:48.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因为叫「露面」  我还以为会有其他人在场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:52.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,还见不到伟大的祖父大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,活人偶已经可以摘下黑纱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:56.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也可以自由聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你们就是这次的五组出席者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那么  让我见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:13.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:20.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,影大人们也很不安  他们也不知如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他会根据我们的表现  给我们分级
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:25.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不能轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喂  你说要见识一下  那我们到底要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,乔恩少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:47.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,既然准备了餐点  那用餐也是自由的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:50.20,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特先喝点茶好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露薏丝也吃点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:56.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我说  你是叫凯特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:57.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:02.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,之前从来没有见过其他的影家人  我还很不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:04.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是吗  那我们好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不  我们不用好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:07.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:11.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你看你看  露薏丝的「脸」是不是很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,对吧  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:18.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我一直很担心能不能得到客观的评价呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你可以多夸夸露薏丝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:23.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,又来了又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你可是一副想多看看我的表情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:30.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露  化了妆之后真的好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,对不起  凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我倒不觉得那是什么很漂亮的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,看看帕利克的脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:44.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,像你这样的  像你这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,一脸假笑  自以为是的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:50.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没错  这种人可做不出我这种表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,太过分了  你的性格太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,差劲？  那可不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克的「脸」连性格都很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,「脸」有性格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:08.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不对  我是说表情也体现出帕利克的性格这点很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是吗  都无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露薏丝小姐上升一层
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:17.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是因为她只把活人偶当做「脸」是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是总觉得那样有些可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:25.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不行  写在遗忘笔记本里了  不要想多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:28.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:35.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,像那时候跟我说话一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:42.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你试试通过食指和影大人说说话怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你知道拉米吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:51.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,小拉米  我也会和一个叫小面包的玩偶说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:59.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您要…喝茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.64,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不好  不小心从凯特小姐身边离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:21.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,「脸」和身体分离了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不要这么杀气腾腾嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:27.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这可是难得的宴会  好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩在好好地当着「脸」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,太好吃了  好吃到想打滚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我让凯特小姐来配合我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什么啊  我还以为你是个冷漠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没想到吃饭的时候就流露真心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我说凯特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,从刚才开始  你的「脸」的表现就很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,而且名字还叫埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:19.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那又怎么了  给「脸」起名字不是很正常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我是按照规定来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可？真是个奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:27.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,一般是取跟自己名字相近的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:31.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那边不吭声的我就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但在这边的全部人都是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:37.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露薏丝和露  乔恩和尚恩  帕利克和利奇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,毕竟是自己的「脸」  这不是理所应当的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:43.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特不喜欢自己的「脸」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这是不被主人爱着的「脸」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:59.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,糟了  再这样貌合神离的话  「露面」会落选的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为什么  埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.37,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为什么她不按我的想法做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我们必须像萨拉和米娅那样做才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:10.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你会想多余的事导致失败
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,会搭理其他的「脸」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:15.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,还因为名字的事动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:19.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,活人偶只作为影家人的「脸」存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:23.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,想多余的事就是对影家人的反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:27.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不管发生什么  都必须对影家人宣誓效忠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:31.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,活人偶之间不需要和睦相处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:45.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真是首优雅的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:49.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,特别的活人偶连钢琴都会弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:55.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他可能是想让我们跳舞  来体现主从合为一体的默契
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.84,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那么我们来跳舞吧  利奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  露薏丝最喜欢跳舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我们练习好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:05.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,对吧  露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:12.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,练习…  我不会跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露薏丝很喜欢自己的「脸」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也就是说她真的很喜欢自己  这一看便知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:25.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她跳舞时引导着露  露也交给她领舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:29.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,相反  帕利克虽然被利奇引导着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:33.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但利奇并不抢风头  让帕利克成为显眼的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,正因为他们性格相近  才会这般默契吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,被拉开差距了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可不能胜任凯特的「脸」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我不能通过「露面」了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可我不想在这里落选
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:49.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特还有要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:19:00.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,一起…跳舞吧  夏丽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:18.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那  我们也去跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:19.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:26.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐  抱歉刚才失落了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:36.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是我搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不曾注视埃米莉可的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我们跳舞吧  埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在那之前  笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:51.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,严肃一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:53.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,笑得夸张一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:02.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这样就好  还是和往常一样的埃米莉可好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:07.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我并不追求影家的正确性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,跟着凯特  我还有秘密特技
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,咦  脚自己动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:20.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,之后都交给凯特就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:28.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可  我现在已经能很好地操控黑灰了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.37,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你还不够好  老是犯错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,无法对有困难的人坐视不管
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,还会想「多余的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你作为活人偶完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:44.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但我觉得  你不循规蹈矩这点很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:48.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,而且你很努力  对谁都很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:51.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,虽然有时候  我也想要你看看我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:15.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:18.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,作为活人偶  这可是对影家人大不敬的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:22.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,再说了  让活人偶来给我们分等级真让我不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,爱德华的主人在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:27.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我是特别的活人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,难道你觉得上级的影家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:33.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,会特意屈尊来见你们这些半吊子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:37.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但你们毕竟是影家人  我当然要尊敬你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:43.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为表歉意  我带各位参观美丽的庭院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:44.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,请来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:47.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好呀  我想看看庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你小子想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:55.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你们就在这吃吃点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:40.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,下集  庭院迷宫
